Thank you very much for explaning, watching from germany here. A couple of my family members in other EU-Countries are really trying me with their argument it is just a regular flu. Thank you very much for explaining from the practical point of view that was really helpful and you described the differences really well.
Any further Ideas or good arguments for them regarding the current vaccine myth's? Maybe you could do a video about debunking some of the stupidest myths I have heard a ton of them, greetz from Berlin and keep up the good work man, appreciate it very much!
